1
00:00:08,007 --> 00:00:12,007
(Kurosaki) ``I love Koharu-san.''

2
00:00:13,513 --> 00:00:15,515
(Koharu) The Yuo-san I know➡

3
00:00:15,515 --> 00:00:18,015
He is a wonderful person who is a hard worker.

4
00:00:20,019 --> 00:00:24,019
I want this happiness to last forever.

5
00:00:30,029 --> 00:00:34,534
Kobun can be learned by knowing the common sense and culture of the time, which was different from the present day➡

6
00:00:34,534 --> 00:00:38,034
It becomes easier to understand the feelings of the characters.

7
00:00:40,540 --> 00:00:42,542
Thanks to Kurosaki-san's explanation➡

8
00:00:42,542 --> 00:00:45,042
I found ``Millow Book'' interesting.

9
00:00:47,046 --> 00:00:50,049
《Kurosaki-san's autograph session ended successfully➡

10
00:00:50,049 --> 00:00:52,552
We have more time to meet each other though.

11
00:00:52,552 --> 00:00:56,055
If you'd like, I'd like to introduce you to some classic literature.

12
00:00:56,055 --> 00:00:58,057
Ah, thank you very much.

13
00:00:58,057 --> 00:01:00,560
I was able to have a popular writer teach me Japanese➡

14
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:02,061
It's a luxury.

15
00:01:02,061 --> 00:01:03,496
No, that's it.

16
00:01:03,496 --> 00:01:04,998
《This time Mr. Kurosaki➡

17
00:01:04,998 --> 00:01:08,001
I was asked to be my Japanese language tutor.

18
00:01:08,001 --> 00:01:11,504
I'll come and teach you as much as I can until the final exam.

19
00:01:11,504 --> 00:01:13,504
thank you.

20
00:01:15,508 --> 00:01:20,013
After the test, take your time...➡

21
00:01:20,013 --> 00:01:22,015
Let's go on a date.

22
00:01:22,015 --> 00:01:24,017
《For love➡

23
00:01:24,017 --> 00:01:27,520
First of all, I have to study hard.》

24
00:01:27,520 --> 00:01:47,540
♬～

25
00:01:47,540 --> 00:02:07,494
♬～

26
00:02:07,494 --> 00:02:23,009
♬～

27
00:02:23,009 --> 00:02:28,009
♬～

28
00:02:38,024 --> 00:02:40,024
That Yuo-san.

29
00:02:42,028 --> 00:02:46,032
Is it okay if I increase the number of shifts a little more?

30
00:02:46,032 --> 00:02:48,034
Until the final exam➡

31
00:02:48,034 --> 00:02:52,038
Kurosaki-san is coming to teach me Japanese.

32
00:02:52,038 --> 00:02:56,042
(Yao) I heard from your brother, what do you think?

33
00:02:56,042 --> 00:02:57,542
picture…?

34
00:02:59,546 --> 00:03:04,484
I don't think I'll be able to concentrate if I learn from my boyfriend.

35
00:03:04,484 --> 00:03:07,487
No, I'll try to do that properly.

36
00:03:07,487 --> 00:03:09,489
Huh…｡

37
00:03:09,489 --> 00:03:12,989
Well, I don't care.

38
00:03:14,994 --> 00:03:19,499
《It seems like Yuio-san has suddenly gotten stronger》

39
00:03:19,499 --> 00:03:21,499
"on second thoughts…"

40
00:03:24,003 --> 00:03:25,503
that.

41
00:03:29,008 --> 00:03:32,011
Meddling on the day of the autograph session.

42
00:03:32,011 --> 00:03:35,014
I'm sorry again.

43
00:03:35,014 --> 00:03:36,514
picture?

44
00:03:37,517 --> 00:03:40,520
I didn't apologize properly.

45
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:45,020
No, I don't really care about that.

46
00:03:54,033 --> 00:03:57,537
Koharu-chan's math grades are improving➡

47
00:03:57,537 --> 00:04:01,040
I was wondering if I could raise the level and make it tougher.

48
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:04,477
Ah... that's right.

49
00:04:04,477 --> 00:04:08,481
Sorry for saying something weird.

50
00:04:08,481 --> 00:04:12,986
Koharu-chan, are you free after school?

51
00:04:12,986 --> 00:04:14,486
Huh?

52
00:04:24,998 --> 00:04:27,500
Yuio-kun, welcome back.

53
00:04:27,500 --> 00:04:29,502
I'm home.

54
00:04:29,502 --> 00:04:31,004
Ah, that's right.

55
00:04:31,004 --> 00:04:35,508
I'll go buy some reference books with Koharu tomorrow.

56
00:04:35,508 --> 00:04:37,008
picture…?

57
00:04:47,520 --> 00:04:51,024
If you have this reference book, getting into the school of your choice will not be a dream.

58
00:04:51,024 --> 00:04:53,024
Is it true? I did it.

59
00:04:54,527 --> 00:04:57,530
There's no point in just buying Koharu-chan.

60
00:04:57,530 --> 00:04:59,532
I... I know.

61
00:04:59,532 --> 00:05:02,035
I'll teach you what you don't understand again.

62
00:05:02,035 --> 00:05:04,435
thank you.

63
00:05:19,986 --> 00:05:22,488
Ah, sorry, thank you.

64
00:05:22,488 --> 00:05:24,991
Yuio-kun, what are you doing to Koharu-san?

65
00:05:24,991 --> 00:05:28,494
picture? yeah? Mr. Kurosaki?

66
00:05:28,494 --> 00:05:31,497
I almost hit the bike, so I just dodged it.

67
00:05:31,497 --> 00:05:33,499
Huh… a bicycle?

68
00:05:33,499 --> 00:05:35,499
(bicycle bell)

69
00:05:37,503 --> 00:05:40,006
What is it, brother? That look.

70
00:05:40,006 --> 00:05:43,509
Ah, uh...➡

71
00:05:43,509 --> 00:05:46,012
Classic literature that I would like to recommend to Koharu ➡

72
00:05:46,012 --> 00:05:48,014
I was thinking of looking for it➡

73
00:05:48,014 --> 00:05:52,518
Just in case, there has been an increase in media exposure lately.

74
00:05:52,518 --> 00:05:55,521
I see, it's difficult for famous people too.

75
00:05:55,521 --> 00:05:57,021
Ah, no...

76
00:05:58,524 --> 00:06:00,526
Don't lie.

77
00:06:00,526 --> 00:06:02,962
It was a nice place.

78
00:06:05,465 --> 00:06:09,969
Well then, I'll go home first, see you soon, Koharu-chan.

79
00:06:09,969 --> 00:06:13,469
Ah yes, thank you for the reference book.

80
00:06:17,477 --> 00:06:21,481
How about the next tutoring session next Sunday?

81
00:06:21,481 --> 00:06:22,982
Oh, I'm sorry.

82
00:06:22,982 --> 00:06:25,985
On that day, Yuio introduced me➡

83
00:06:25,985 --> 00:06:29,489
I was supposed to meet an alumnus of the school I wanted to go to.

84
00:06:29,489 --> 00:06:30,990
Desired school?

85
00:06:30,990 --> 00:06:32,492
yes.

86
00:06:32,492 --> 00:06:36,496
Graduated from a school where you can study restaurant management➡

87
00:06:36,496 --> 00:06:38,498
For those who run a cafe restaurant➡

88
00:06:38,498 --> 00:06:40,998
He told me a lot of stories.

89
00:06:42,502 --> 00:06:47,006
Are you going with Yuo?

90
00:06:47,006 --> 00:06:50,506
Yes, Yuio-san is also interested.

91
00:06:52,011 --> 00:06:54,013
Ah, if you don't like Kurosaki-san, go by yourself.

92
00:06:54,013 --> 00:06:58,513
That's nice! Please enjoy it.

93
00:07:01,020 --> 00:07:03,456
Oh, I'll study hard for the test too.

94
00:07:03,456 --> 00:07:08,456
I'm really looking forward to my date with Kurosaki-san.

95
00:07:13,466 --> 00:07:17,470
After the test, you'll go on a leisurely date, right?

96
00:07:17,470 --> 00:07:19,970
I will do my best for that.

97
00:07:24,977 --> 00:07:26,979
(The sound of running footsteps)

98
00:07:26,979 --> 00:07:28,481
Haha.

99
00:07:28,481 --> 00:07:29,981
picture…?

100
00:07:32,485 --> 00:07:34,987
I'm also looking forward to the date.

101
00:07:34,987 --> 00:07:39,492
This... is this outside?

102
00:07:39,492 --> 00:07:40,993
already….

103
00:07:40,993 --> 00:07:43,493
I... I'm sorry.

104
00:07:44,997 --> 00:07:49,997
It's okay here, then.

105
00:07:51,504 --> 00:07:54,507
《Hah... I was so excited》

106
00:07:54,507 --> 00:07:58,507
《Today seemed more sudden than usual...》

107
00:08:00,012 --> 00:08:02,949
《Even though we are so close➡

108
00:08:02,949 --> 00:08:05,849
Why is my heart racing?

109
00:08:17,965 --> 00:08:19,967
Thank you for the meal.

110
00:08:19,967 --> 00:08:21,969
(Anna) How was it? My meal.

111
00:08:21,969 --> 00:08:25,472
Gentle and careful cuisine that brings out the flavors of the ingredients➡

112
00:08:25,472 --> 00:08:29,977
I'm happy both physically and mentally.Thank you for the meal, Anna.

113
00:08:29,977 --> 00:08:31,979
The tension is too high.

114
00:08:31,979 --> 00:08:33,914
Ah, sorry.

115
00:08:33,914 --> 00:08:37,418
Wow, thank you for your kind and enthusiastic review.

116
00:08:37,418 --> 00:08:41,422
So you want to join a food business course?

117
00:08:41,422 --> 00:08:44,425
Are you planning to take over the store in the future?

118
00:08:44,425 --> 00:08:47,428
I hope I can pass it on.

119
00:08:47,428 --> 00:08:51,432
Our store was created by my late mother➡

120
00:08:51,432 --> 00:08:54,935
I also want to preserve my mother's taste➡

121
00:08:54,935 --> 00:08:58,939
I wish I could be like my mother.

122
00:08:58,939 --> 00:09:01,442
Like your mother?

123
00:09:01,442 --> 00:09:02,943
yes.

124
00:09:02,943 --> 00:09:07,448
My mother always said that she wanted to make everyone smile with her cooking.

125
00:09:07,448 --> 00:09:11,952
(2 people) ((It's delicious, it's delicious))

126
00:09:11,952 --> 00:09:14,452
(Four seasons)((Itadakimasu))

127
00:09:15,956 --> 00:09:19,460
(Four seasons)((Yes, it's delicious!))

128
00:09:19,460 --> 00:09:22,463
((Koharu genius!)) ((Really?))

129
00:09:22,463 --> 00:09:24,465
((Will I be like my mother?))

130
00:09:24,465 --> 00:09:25,966
((I can become it))

131
00:09:25,966 --> 00:09:29,470
((Mom, I'm really happy now))

132
00:09:29,470 --> 00:09:33,474
(Koharu's voice) I'm also happy that my mother is happy➡

133
00:09:33,474 --> 00:09:36,874
I started to like cooking more and more.

134
00:09:39,913 --> 00:09:44,413
I can't see my mother's smile anymore...

135
00:09:45,919 --> 00:09:47,921
Are you okay?

136
00:09:47,921 --> 00:09:52,426
Sorry, I just remembered.

137
00:09:52,426 --> 00:09:56,430
Mom and cooking➡

138
00:09:56,430 --> 00:09:58,930
I love it.

139
00:10:01,935 --> 00:10:05,935
Look, you have an ugly face.

140
00:10:09,443 --> 00:10:11,945
I'll borrow the restroom.

141
00:10:11,945 --> 00:10:17,951
♬～

142
00:10:17,951 --> 00:10:21,455
Yuio-kun is very kind to Koharu-chan.

143
00:10:21,455 --> 00:10:22,956
teeth?

144
00:10:22,956 --> 00:10:25,956
"Be kind to others" is my motto.

145
00:10:27,961 --> 00:10:29,461
(sound of door opening)

146
00:10:30,964 --> 00:10:33,467
welcome home.

147
00:10:33,467 --> 00:10:35,367
I'm home.

148
00:10:36,403 --> 00:10:40,407
Yuio introduced me to the cafe manager➡

149
00:10:40,407 --> 00:10:42,910
I asked Koharu-san.

150
00:10:42,910 --> 00:10:45,913
I heard that he is offering advice on career options.

151
00:10:45,913 --> 00:10:48,916
thank you.

152
00:10:48,916 --> 00:10:51,418
It's not especially for my brother.

153
00:10:51,418 --> 00:10:53,418
I agree.

154
00:10:55,422 --> 00:10:58,926
But Yuo-kun also goes to university, part-time job, and tutoring➡

155
00:10:58,926 --> 00:11:00,928
Isn't it difficult?

156
00:11:00,928 --> 00:11:03,928
Are you really worried about me?

157
00:11:06,433 --> 00:11:08,433
Of course.

158
00:11:10,938 --> 00:11:14,441
It's okay, I'm having fun.

159
00:11:14,441 --> 00:11:18,946
Koharu-chan was really happy today too.

160
00:11:18,946 --> 00:11:22,950
Along the way, I remembered my mother and started crying.

161
00:11:22,950 --> 00:11:24,451
picture?

162
00:11:24,451 --> 00:11:27,955
Something feels like I can't leave it alone anymore.

163
00:11:27,955 --> 00:11:33,460
I decided to support Koharu-chan.

164
00:11:33,460 --> 00:11:35,395
(Sound of glass being placed)

165
00:11:35,395 --> 00:11:37,898
(footsteps)

166
00:11:37,898 --> 00:11:39,399
(sound of door closing)

167
00:11:39,399 --> 00:11:41,401
Here is the gift ➡

168
00:11:41,401 --> 00:11:45,405
Koharu special energetic bento.

169
00:11:45,405 --> 00:11:47,908
It's extremely ecstatic!

170
00:11:47,908 --> 00:11:49,408
What... please.

171
00:11:50,911 --> 00:11:52,913
I'll enjoy having this.

172
00:11:52,913 --> 00:11:59,920
♬～

173
00:11:59,920 --> 00:12:02,422
Entertain many people➡

174
00:12:02,422 --> 00:12:05,926
It's amazing how happy novelists are.

175
00:12:05,926 --> 00:12:07,928
Although the scale is completely different ➡

176
00:12:07,928 --> 00:12:12,432
I too wish I could bring happiness through cooking.

177
00:12:12,432 --> 00:12:14,935
I talked to OG Anna the other day➡

178
00:12:14,935 --> 00:12:17,437
That feeling has become even stronger.

179
00:12:17,437 --> 00:12:20,941
That was more than anything.

180
00:12:20,941 --> 00:12:23,944
Ah, but there was a bit of a failure...

181
00:12:23,944 --> 00:12:25,946
We were talking about the shop➡

182
00:12:25,946 --> 00:12:28,448
I cried a little as I remembered my mother.

183
00:12:28,448 --> 00:12:30,948
It was embarrassing.

184
00:12:33,887 --> 00:12:36,787
((Because I decided to support Koharu-chan))

185
00:12:43,897 --> 00:12:45,399
No.

186
00:12:45,399 --> 00:12:50,404
No... What's wrong?

187
00:12:50,404 --> 00:12:54,408
Ah... haha ​​It's nothing.

188
00:12:54,408 --> 00:12:55,909
picture?

189
00:12:55,909 --> 00:12:58,912
Haha... Those Koharu-san's tears➡

190
00:12:58,912 --> 00:13:01,915
I thought I wanted to wipe it➡

191
00:13:01,915 --> 00:13:04,418
I just made a joke.

192
00:13:04,418 --> 00:13:06,918
Ahahahahaha...

193
00:13:09,423 --> 00:13:12,926
But something was wrong the other day...

194
00:13:12,926 --> 00:13:14,928
Ah... Koharu-san.

195
00:13:14,928 --> 00:13:16,930
It's really a boring joke➡

196
00:13:16,930 --> 00:13:19,430
Please forget it.

197
00:13:24,438 --> 00:13:28,942
Even though you look like that, I can't believe it's a joke.

198
00:13:28,942 --> 00:13:32,446
If Kurosaki-san➡

199
00:13:32,446 --> 00:13:35,382
If you can't tell me how you feel➡

200
00:13:35,382 --> 00:13:37,882
I'm a little lonely.

201
00:13:43,390 --> 00:13:47,394
Sorry for saying something so arrogant.

202
00:13:47,394 --> 00:13:50,897
I have to study for a test, so I'm going home today.

203
00:13:50,897 --> 00:13:53,897
Yeah?

204
00:13:57,404 --> 00:13:59,406
《I feel lonely➡

205
00:13:59,406 --> 00:14:03,406
Am I a child who runs away after venting my feelings?

206
00:14:06,413 --> 00:14:08,415
Koharu-san!

207
00:14:08,415 --> 00:14:10,917
Sigh… Sigh…｡

208
00:14:10,917 --> 00:14:12,919
Kurosaki-san, are you okay?

209
00:14:12,919 --> 00:14:16,419
Ah, no, I came at full speed...

210
00:14:19,426 --> 00:14:21,428
that….

211
00:14:21,428 --> 00:14:23,928
(2 people) I'm sorry.

212
00:14:25,432 --> 00:14:26,932
(2 people) Huh?

213
00:14:27,934 --> 00:14:30,937
What... why is Kurosaki-san apologizing?

214
00:14:30,937 --> 00:14:35,375
That's this line.

215
00:14:35,375 --> 00:14:37,878
Huh... that...

216
00:14:37,878 --> 00:14:40,380
The words and actions from earlier.

217
00:14:40,380 --> 00:14:44,384
As Koharu-san said, this is not a joke.

218
00:14:44,384 --> 00:14:46,386
picture?

219
00:14:46,386 --> 00:14:49,890
I listened to Koharu-san's story➡

220
00:14:49,890 --> 00:14:53,894
I couldn't control my jealousy towards Yuo-kun.

221
00:14:53,894 --> 00:14:57,397
She's just doing her best for Koharu-san➡

222
00:14:57,397 --> 00:15:02,897
The closer the two of us become, the more our hearts become agitated...

223
00:15:07,407 --> 00:15:10,410
Such an unsightly feeling➡

224
00:15:10,410 --> 00:15:13,410
I didn't want Koharu-san to see it.

225
00:15:17,417 --> 00:15:20,420
You're with me.

226
00:15:20,420 --> 00:15:21,920
picture?

227
00:15:22,923 --> 00:15:29,930
I was also jealous of Mr. Arisugawa and worried alone.

228
00:15:29,930 --> 00:15:34,368
But that's what Kurosaki-san told me at that time.

229
00:15:34,368 --> 00:15:37,371
It's okay to be spoiled.

230
00:15:37,371 --> 00:15:41,871
That's why I also want Kurosaki-san to be kind to me.

231
00:15:43,377 --> 00:15:48,382
But I guess it's not me.

232
00:15:48,382 --> 00:15:51,385
I miss that.

233
00:15:51,385 --> 00:15:56,385
So I'm glad you told me your true feelings.

234
00:16:01,395 --> 00:16:05,899
I'm sorry for making Koharu-san feel lonely.

235
00:16:05,899 --> 00:16:10,399
Thank you for accepting me even though I am like this.

236
00:16:12,906 --> 00:16:17,906
Let's aim to be lovers who can communicate our true feelings to each other.

237
00:16:20,914 --> 00:16:23,414
I've got it.

238
00:16:26,920 --> 00:16:29,923
《I was so confused➡

239
00:16:29,923 --> 00:16:33,423
Thanks to Koharu-san, my heart feels better》

240
00:16:35,362 --> 00:16:39,362
《If only Yuo and I could face each other honestly...》

241
00:16:41,868 --> 00:16:46,372
(Mika) Will Koharu go on many dates with Kurosaki-san during spring break?

242
00:16:46,372 --> 00:16:47,874
Hehe…｡ Hehehe.

243
00:16:47,874 --> 00:16:51,377
(Riri) She'll be a third year high school student soon, but she won't have time to play like that.

244
00:16:51,377 --> 00:16:52,812
That's right.

245
00:16:52,812 --> 00:16:56,315
Koharu will continue to be your tutor, right?

246
00:16:56,315 --> 00:16:59,819
That's right, I have to study.

247
00:16:59,819 --> 00:17:02,822
That's it...

248
00:17:02,822 --> 00:17:05,825
I was thinking about going to a cram school or something.

249
00:17:05,825 --> 00:17:07,326
Is that so?

250
00:17:07,326 --> 00:17:11,831
Well, it's true that you might not be able to concentrate if your boyfriend is teaching you something.

251
00:17:11,831 --> 00:17:17,837
♬～

252
00:17:17,837 --> 00:17:19,839
(Mika) For Koharu➡

253
00:17:19,839 --> 00:17:22,341
My boyfriend's younger brother also taught me this➡

254
00:17:22,341 --> 00:17:24,343
Aren't you curious?

255
00:17:24,343 --> 00:17:27,847
Look, it looks like Kurosaki-san is grilling mochiyaki.

256
00:17:27,847 --> 00:17:31,350
As expected! Something feels a little awkward...

257
00:17:31,350 --> 00:17:32,850
slow!

258
00:17:34,353 --> 00:17:36,353
If you spread rumors...

259
00:17:37,857 --> 00:17:39,859
Thank you for your hard work on the test.

260
00:17:39,859 --> 00:17:44,363
I studied hard and it's a reward.

261
00:17:44,363 --> 00:17:47,363
Are you planning to go to karaoke with us?

262
00:17:48,868 --> 00:17:50,868
Are you okay.

263
00:17:54,807 --> 00:17:57,310
Yuio-san.

264
00:17:57,310 --> 00:18:02,315
I actually have something I'd like to talk to you about.

265
00:18:02,315 --> 00:18:03,815
picture?

266
00:18:09,322 --> 00:18:10,823
Which one would you choose?

267
00:18:10,823 --> 00:18:14,327
Well, what should I do...

268
00:18:14,327 --> 00:18:17,327
What about that Kurosaki-san?

269
00:18:18,831 --> 00:18:20,833
I'm going to the publisher today.

270
00:18:20,833 --> 00:18:23,333
Ah, that's right.

271
00:18:26,839 --> 00:18:30,343
Maybe you don't like sweets?

272
00:18:30,343 --> 00:18:32,345
No, I love it.

273
00:18:32,345 --> 00:18:35,848
I wonder if it's okay for me to do something like this.

274
00:18:35,848 --> 00:18:37,850
Don't hesitate to choose.

275
00:18:37,850 --> 00:18:42,855
Well, it was difficult to teach because it was so clunky➡

276
00:18:42,855 --> 00:18:45,355
I think you did a good job.

277
00:18:47,360 --> 00:18:49,862
Um... about that➡

278
00:18:49,862 --> 00:18:53,299
There is something I would like to talk to Yuo-san.

279
00:18:53,299 --> 00:18:56,802
Ah, now that I think about it, did something happen?

280
00:18:56,802 --> 00:19:02,302
I thought about it in my own way.

281
00:19:03,809 --> 00:19:08,314
From now on, I thought I'd try my best to study on my own.

282
00:19:08,314 --> 00:19:10,316
picture?

283
00:19:10,316 --> 00:19:14,320
Does that mean I should stop being a tutor?

284
00:19:14,320 --> 00:19:16,822
I don't want to be spoiled any more.

285
00:19:16,822 --> 00:19:19,325
No, my grades just improved➡

286
00:19:19,325 --> 00:19:21,327
Are you not feeling well?

287
00:19:21,327 --> 00:19:26,332
Studying for entrance exams isn't easy enough for Koharu to do on her own.

288
00:19:26,332 --> 00:19:30,336
I know that, but...

289
00:19:30,336 --> 00:19:34,836
Maybe... brother?

290
00:19:36,342 --> 00:19:38,344
Did he say something?

291
00:19:38,344 --> 00:19:41,847
No, that's not it. If so, why?

292
00:19:41,847 --> 00:19:45,851
I have seen Koharu-chan working hard from close up➡

293
00:19:45,851 --> 00:19:48,854
I want to continue to support you!

294
00:19:48,854 --> 00:19:50,354
picture?

295
00:19:51,857 --> 00:19:56,295
Ah... Shit... What did I say?

296
00:19:56,295 --> 00:19:59,799
What do you mean, I want to support you?

297
00:19:59,799 --> 00:20:02,301
Don't you understand?

298
00:20:02,301 --> 00:20:04,303
That's really stupid!

299
00:20:04,303 --> 00:20:07,807
Eh... I'm sorry, I was too blunt...

300
00:20:07,807 --> 00:20:09,809
Ah~ Um...｡

301
00:20:09,809 --> 00:20:13,309
Ah, oh... what about the store? Ah, already!

302
00:20:14,313 --> 00:20:17,313
It means I love you!

303
00:20:18,818 --> 00:20:20,820
What?!

304
00:20:20,820 --> 00:20:25,820
Koharu-chan looked at me.

305
00:20:27,326 --> 00:20:31,831
Not as his younger brother, but as myself.

306
00:20:31,831 --> 00:20:36,335
I want you to see more of me➡

307
00:20:36,335 --> 00:20:39,338
I want to see it too.

308
00:20:39,338 --> 00:20:47,847
♬～

309
00:20:47,847 --> 00:20:50,349
Yuio-san…➡

310
00:20:50,349 --> 00:20:56,288
Although he is strict, he is a wonderful person who is reliable.

311
00:20:56,288 --> 00:20:59,792
But I...If that's the case, choose it!

312
00:20:59,792 --> 00:21:02,294
Not him, but me.

313
00:21:02,294 --> 00:21:10,803
♬～

314
00:21:10,803 --> 00:21:15,303
Yuio-san, I'm sorry.

315
00:21:18,811 --> 00:21:23,811
I... I like Kurosaki-san.

316
00:21:29,321 --> 00:21:41,821
Smartphone) (vibrating sound)

317
00:21:44,336 --> 00:21:46,839
Yuio-kun, where are you now?

318
00:21:46,839 --> 00:21:48,841
Smartphone) I'm home, but what?

319
00:21:48,841 --> 00:21:52,344
I'm currently on my way back from the publisher➡

320
00:21:52,344 --> 00:21:55,281
Can we talk at home?

321
00:21:55,281 --> 00:21:57,283
Smartphone) Talk?

322
00:21:57,283 --> 00:22:00,786
I haven't been able to tell Yuio my true feelings for a long time.

323
00:22:00,786 --> 00:22:04,290
And please let me know your true feelings.

324
00:22:04,290 --> 00:22:07,790
Huh? Really?

325
00:22:12,298 --> 00:22:15,301
Yuio-san, what happened?

326
00:22:15,301 --> 00:22:19,305
Current voice: Is Koharu-san also here?

327
00:22:19,305 --> 00:22:21,305
Are you serious...?

328
00:22:22,808 --> 00:22:26,808
There's something I wanted to say too.

329
00:22:28,814 --> 00:22:33,314
Past and present, I have always been...

330
00:22:34,820 --> 00:22:37,320
I hate you.

331
00:22:41,327 --> 00:22:46,827
So from now on, I'm going to destroy something important to you.

332
00:22:48,834 --> 00:22:51,337
I hope you make it in time.

333
00:22:51,337 --> 00:22:53,272
big brother.

334
00:22:53,272 --> 00:22:54,773
♬～

335
00:22:54,773 --> 00:22:56,275
♬～Smartphone) (operation sound)

336
00:22:56,275 --> 00:23:13,792
♬～

337
00:23:13,792 --> 00:23:15,792
Yuio-san?
